assets.name: assets/8mrI8Kw-L2P
assets.description: It has a clustered system of organization. It is the transformation of the cubic form. The color turns into the darker orange step by step. At the end there is a big rectangular prism which is the most reddish orange. It is not a complete shape but because of the defined spaces, the shape can clearly be seen. I used 6 squares and they all have the same scale. I used 5 rectangles, and their small side has the same size with the size of sides of the squares. Color is chosen to show the transformation. For the transformation yellow was not enough. There had to be an another color being added to the main color.  The second color was red which was being added more and more in every step.

assets.name: assets/fUJu9qj-Tkg
assets.description: It has a gridal system of organization. The model shows the transformation of planar elements into a solid object but it does not directly becomes a cubic form. Rather than that it reflexes the idea of a formation of cubic form. The colors are chosen to highlight the idea that for transformation, there should be something that is being added or distracted . Thus yellow turned into white by adding white and turned into red by adding red. From every perspective only one hue is seen and it forms a big square.
